org.apache.flink.streaming.runtime.operators.windowing

类 EvictingWindowOperator.EvictorContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.runtime.operators.windowing.EvictingWindowOperator.EvictorContext

    封闭类:
    EvictingWindowOperator<K,IN,OUT,W extends Window>

    class EvictingWindowOperator.EvictorContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements Evictor.EvictorContext
    EvictorContext is a utility for handling Evictor invocations. It can be reused by setting the key and window fields. No internal state must be kept in the EvictorContext.

      • getMetricGroup

        public MetricGroup getMetricGroup()
        从接口复制的说明: Evictor.EvictorContext
        Returns the metric group for this Evictor. This is the same metric group that would be returned from RuntimeContext.getMetricGroup() in a user function.

        You must not call methods that create metric objects (such as MetricGroup.counter(int) multiple times but instead call once and store the metric object in a field.

        指定者:
        getMetricGroup 在接口中 Evictor.EvictorContext
